We're using the VL6180 TOF range sensor
A 16-channel Analog Multiplexer will serve to MUX several VL6180s together.
An iterative loop will collect and display data from sensors simulteneously

See "multi_vl6180_controller_mux_example.ino"
See "VL6180_test.py"

As of 03/25/2017 we have a raspberry pi 3 running Pypy, with 

dependencies
smbus module
ST_VL6180X.py module

To install smbus use:

pip3 install smbus-cffi
  
